#: ../../content/applications/hr/lunch/products.rst:45
msgid ""
"In the **Lunch** app, there are four default categories: "
":guilabel:`Sandwich`, :guilabel:`Pizza`, :guilabel:`Burger`, and "
":guilabel:`Drinks`."
