msgstr "Schritte zur Einrichtung des SD-Worx-Moduls"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2889
msgid ""
"You must be logged into a Belgian company for the following steps to work."
msgstr ""
